[ Presentation ]
----------------
Draws some random walks. Programmed in C++ with SDL and OpenGL.

[ Compiling ]
-------------
Once the archive unzipped, go into the root directory and type `make'.

[ Using ]
---------
Launch the main program by typing `./main'.

[ Documentation ]
-----------------
For any extra information, please consult the documentation with `make doc'.
